<bioghist encodinganalog="545$a">
<head>Biographical/Historical Information 
</head>
<p>Vinton Valentine was partner, then sole owner and operator of Valentine Coal Company on Preston Avenue, Charlottesville, Va.
</p>
</bioghist>
<scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a">
<head>Scope and Content
</head>
<p>Photographs of Vinton Valentine; Valentine Coal Store Front; 1935 McGuffey School Graduation Class; Nancy Gordon Private School Class; Bell Telephone Employees of Wheeling, West Virginia; Portrait of Vinton Hope Valentine; Home on 305 High Street. Paper items include: Valentine Coal Company letterhead; photocopy of Valentine Coal Co. advertisement; and 1934 McGuffy Reader.
</p>
</scopecontent>

